trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"></xref> column that hosts <xref:System.Uri> elements in its cells.
trans-unit.target: 代表<xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"></xref>裝載的資料行<xref:System.Uri>中其儲存格的項目。</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Use DataGridHyperlinkColumn to display data that contains a <xref:System.Uri>, such as an HTTP address or e-mail address.
trans-unit.target: 若要顯示包含的資料使用 DataGridHyperlinkColumn <xref:System.Uri>，例如 HTTP 地址或電子郵件地址。</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows an example of a DataGridHyperlinkColumn.
trans-unit.target: 下圖顯示 DataGridHyperlinkColumn 的範例。

trans-unit.source: ![DataGridHyperlinkColumn with email addresses](~/add/media/wpf-hyperlinkcolumn.png "DataGridHyperlinkColumn with email addresses") > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> navigation can only occur if either the direct or indirect parent of a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> is a navigation host.
trans-unit.target: ![電子郵件地址的 DataGridHyperlinkColumn](~/add/media/wpf-hyperlinkcolumn.png "電子郵件地址的 DataGridHyperlinkColumn") > [!NOTE] ><xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>當其中一個，才可以進行瀏覽的直接或間接父系<xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>是瀏覽的主機。</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: Examples of navigation hosts include <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, or any browser that can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)], such as [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)] or later and Firefox 2.0 or later.
trans-unit.target: 巡覽裝載的範例包括<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>， <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>，或可以裝載任何瀏覽器[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)]，例如[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)]或更新版本和 Firefox 2.0 或更新版本。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "Navigation Hosts" topic in [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱中的 瀏覽主機 」 主題[巡覽概觀](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: To populate the column, bind the column to the <xref:System.Uri> data by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要填入資料行，資料行繫結至<xref:System.Uri>資料使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> </xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: To display hyperlink text that is different than the URI string, bind the text value to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要顯示不同的 URI 字串的超連結文字，繫結的文字值<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property is applied to the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> element created in the column.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>屬性會套用到<xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>或<xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>建立資料行中的項目。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A> for the element in each cell is the data item for the row the cell is in.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>每個資料格中的項目是資料列儲存格的資料項目是。</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, to set up the binding you only have to set the <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，若要設定繫結只需要設定<xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Optionally, you can specify a <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName> if you want to convert the data.
trans-unit.target: 您可以選擇性地指定<xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>如果您想要將資料轉換。</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information about data binding, see [Data Binding (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需資料繫結的詳細資訊，請參閱[資料繫結 (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > DataGridHyperlinkColumn creates a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> element in the non-editing mode and a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> element in the editing mode.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > DataGridHyperlinkColumn 建立<xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>非編輯模式中的項目和<xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>編輯模式中的項目。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: If you want to display other types of data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> provides the following column types: |Column Type|Data Display| |-----------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>|Use to display Boolean data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>|Use to display enumeration data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>|Use to display text.| If you want to use other controls in your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>, you can create your own column types by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.
trans-unit.target: 如果您想要顯示其他類型的資料，<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>會提供下列資料行類型: |資料行類型 |資料顯示 | |-----------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>|用來顯示布林值資料。 | |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>|用來顯示列舉型別資料。 | |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>|用於顯示文字。 | 如果您想要在程式中<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>，您可以建立自己的資料行型別使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn></xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>使用其他控制項</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn></xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn></xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn></xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>

trans-unit.target: 會導致還原指定的值為正在編輯的資料行儲存格。

trans-unit.target: 先前未編輯的值所編輯的儲存格。
